pull_request.title: Runtime deviations checking
pull_request.body:
Fixes #27. 20% set as threshold.

Notifications are sent by email to the comma separated list of recipients encoded in https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/blob/5feb858c45dcd7f0d1405b0ae3e2532eec65da52/perf/scripts/notify.py#L8

Full deviations report is stored in S3.
